translated: Joachimsson, Åke, estate manager, Linköping, b. 12/12/79 in Bankekind, östergötl. 1., son of Nils J. and Hilma Stånggren. Married to Olga Ekstam in 19xx. Children: Karin b. 15, Olof b. 17, Wilhelm b. 22. Graduated from the forestry institute forest master's course in 01. County hunting master in östergötl. from 08-16, estate manager at Baroniet Adelswärd in Åtvidaberg from 16-27, owner and operator of Lerboga in Bankekind parish, manages several estates in östergötl. 1. Member of the östergötl. 1. forestry board since 18, chairman of Bankekind road board from 25-43, member of Bankekind household guild since 29, östergötl. L. Fire Insurance Company since 34, Accident Insurance Company Egid since 43, resident representative since 32, member of the board for the Skand. Bank's branch office in Linköp. since 32, vice chairman of municipal council and municipal board, church warden, etc. Writings: Save on domestic timber (08), Forest management of small-scale agriculture (19) and more. RVO.
